{"tid":523713,"cid":18,"subCid":0,"title":"其實共產主義對世界有乜貢獻過？係咪唔出現會更好？","createTime":"2018-01-09T00:20:15.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-10T03:58:10.000Z","uid":57376,"like":73,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":53,"replies":[{"pid":"54d9da0b9224294485f30a35e0b298794debb24e","tid":523713,"uid":57376,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:20:15.000Z","msg":"先唔講馬克斯本身係為勞工著想<br />\n佢個主義真係未見其利先見其害<br />\n蘇聯，中共，北韓，全部都利用佢個&quot;願境&quot;去呃低下階層幫佢地打天下，結果有眼睇，大肅清，文革，饑荒，全部都係人禍<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n但如果無共產主義，無蘇聯，納粹德國係咪就唔會滅亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9d188b5b89b4e5717542e0a563dda56f8c837439","tid":523713,"uid":41355,"like":6,"dislike":1,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:22:36.000Z","msg":"宗教<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b7b1822258af4a6a5ccb4e683a8bea6dea3d530d","tid":523713,"uid":126220,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:28:17.000Z","msg":"但係兩登仔最想共產不勞而獲人人一層樓wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"76509ea5af5084b4ae5e37d00686a0de3b54d050","tid":523713,"uid":92498,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:28:56.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"dbb87d78fdd30fb95f78a5e61832d0f7b64a3d1b","tid":523713,"uid":165195,"like":32,"dislike":0,"score":32,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:30:30.000Z","msg":"其實馬克思都無實際講過共產社會/政權實際運作係點,之後嘅共產政權只不過係野心家自己整出嚟,而且好多極權統治例如北韓咁都係扭曲盧梭個社會契約論嚟欺騙人民,好似佢地會自稱人民導師咁,所以馬克思主義應該係比較貼近工作上嘅民主制度,e.g合作社,而唔係一個用係治國嘅政治思想?<br />\n利申:鳩Up"},{"pid":"f918e577adaab056ec0a80050559e356963b3b21","tid":523713,"uid":57376,"like":8,"dislike":1,"score":7,"quote":{"pid":"b7b1822258af4a6a5ccb4e683a8bea6dea3d530d","tid":523713,"uid":126220,"like":28,"dislike":0,"score":28,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-01-09T00:28:17.000Z","msg":"但係兩登仔最想共產不勞而獲人人一層樓wor<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/05.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"ci